        <title type="html"><![CDATA[非「少数民族寄宿制中小学和幼儿园」只需要建立「清真灶和专卖窗口」]]></title>
        <id>https://hihaixiaodai.github.io/post/fei-shao-shu-min-zu-ji-su-zhi-zhong-xiao-xue-he-you-er-yuan-zhi-xu-yao-jian-li-qing-zhen-zao-he-zhuan-mai-chuang-kou/</id>
        <link href="https://hihaixiaodai.github.io/post/fei-shao-shu-min-zu-ji-su-zhi-zhong-xiao-xue-he-you-er-yuan-zhi-xu-yao-jian-li-qing-zhen-zao-he-zhuan-mai-chuang-kou/">
